---
title: New from Driscoll Brook Press
layout: article
---
%section.post-list
  - page_articles.select{|book| book.data[:available] && book.data.available == 'Now'}.sort{|a,b| a.date <=> b.date}.last.tap do|book|
    %article.post
      = partial "layouts/book/header", locals: {book: book}
      = partial "layouts/book/body", locals: {body: book.body}
      = partial "layouts/book/purchase", locals: {book: book.data}
